          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--5" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=0;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="解压后，使用./repo.sh运行repo脚本(RK官方使用repo来管理多仓库的git项目)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="70" width="130" x="72.5" y="275" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--10" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--7" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--9" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--7" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=0;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="编译SDK前先检查ubuntu的资源是否受限(推荐：最低磁盘容&amp;gt;=100GB;ubuntu虚拟机内存大小:&amp;gt;8GB,最低4GB（4G的话，需搭配swap交换空间去使用）；处理器核心数:根据物理机情况越多越好);编译时间大概1.5~2小时，受磁盘类型(SSD、机械)、虚拟机内存大小、虚拟机核心数影响。&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 51, 51); font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;注意：不要用root权限解压和编译SDK；不要用sudo模式解压SDK；不要将SDK解压到中文路径下。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="200" width="165" x="55" y="385" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--12" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--9" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--11" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--9" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font&gt;编译前，将ubuntu的镜像源切换到国内的阿里云(mirror.aliyun.com)；然后安装一些常用的必须的库：&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;apt-get install git ssh make gcc libssl-dev&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;liblz4-tool expect expect-dev g++ patchelf chrpath gawk texinfo chrpath&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 10.56pt; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;cmake gcc-multilib g++-multilib unzip device-tree-compiler ncurses-dev&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;等(具体安装项可参考正点原子pdf:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;ATK-DLRV1126B_SDK开发手册V1.0.pdf&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;)。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;sudo apt-get install &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;gettext &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;# &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;提供的 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;Ubuntu20 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;虚拟机还需要装这个&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;sudo apt-get install clang-format # &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;如果是 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;Ubuntu24 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;还要装这个&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="205.5" width="235" x="20" y="635" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--14" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--11" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--13">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--11" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="SDK目录有以下文件夹：&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 10.56pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;app&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 10.56pt; font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 10.56pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;buildroot&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 10.56pt; font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 10.56pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;device&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 10.56pt; font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 10.56pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;external&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 10.56pt; font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 10.56pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;tools&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 10.56pt; font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 10.56pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;u-boot、kernel、 rockdev、build.sh等多个目录和文件。&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="190" x="42.5" y="895" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--16" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--13" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--15" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--13" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="build.sh就是编译脚本，可一键全编译SDK，也可单独编译uboot、kernel、buildroot文件系统，执行build.sh&amp;nbsp; -h 可罗列出所有的功能" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90" width="140" x="400" y="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--18" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--15" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--17" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--15" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;执行 ./build.sh&amp;nbsp; lunch来&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;指定 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;SDK &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;的板级配置文件&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="50" width="135" x="402.5" y="215" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--23" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--17" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--22" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--17" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;输入一个序号来选择板级配置文件&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;板级文件的作用是配置&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;不同的设备树、不同的内核配置和不同的文件系统类型以适配不同类型的开发板&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: 瀹嬩綋;&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="100" width="150" x="395" y="315" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--19" parent="1" style="shape=curlyBracket;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=1;labelPosition=left;verticalLabelPosition=middle;align=right;verticalAlign=middle;direction=west;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="240" width="10" x="550" y="125" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--21" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;horizontal=1;textDirection=vertical-lr;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;只需要配置一次，下次直接./build.sh&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="220" width="42.5" x="545" y="145" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--25" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--22" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--24" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--22" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="&lt;font&gt;执行 ./build.sh 开始编译整个SDK(大约1.5~3小时编完，生成的目标镜像文件位于SDK的rockdev目录下面，并且全是一些软链接文件，然后使用&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;RKDevToo工具按照烧录相关文档烧录即可&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="145" x="397.5" y="460" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--32" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--24" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--31" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--24" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;rounded=0;" value="&lt;b&gt;下面开始AI相关的配置和开发环境搭建&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="42.25" width="130" x="405" y="627.75" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--30" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--29" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--4" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--29" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;开始&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="120" x="78" y="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--34" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--31" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--33" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--31" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="安装交叉编译工具链：在SDK中执行：./build.sh bsdk。然后生成的工具链在SDK:/buildroot/output/具体平台xxx/host中,将host文件夹打包成xx.tar.gz后，解码到其他路径下，需要执行host/relocate-sdk.sh脚本，工具链才生效。" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="133.87" width="162.5" x="388.75" y="720" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--36" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--33" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--35">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--33" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;align=left;" value="&lt;font&gt;从清华镜像库网站下载anaconda：&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.c&lt;br&gt;n/anaconda/archive/?C=M&amp;amp;O=D,比如：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Anac&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;onda3-2023.03-1-Linux-x86_64.sh，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="77.5" width="215" x="362.5" y="922.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--38" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--35" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--37" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--35" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;执行以下命令，修改&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;conda &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;环境变量去设置每次开机后不自动进入 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;conda&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;的虚拟环境：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.45pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;conda config --set auto_activate_base false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="70" width="280" x="726.25" y="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--40" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--37" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--39" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--37" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;align=center;" value="执行以下指令更改anaconda环境的下载源从国外更改到国内：&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.45pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;conda config --add channels &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.45pt;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,255);&quot;&gt;https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/main/&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.45pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;conda config --add channels &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.45pt;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,255);&quot;&gt;https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/free/&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.45pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;conda config --add channels &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.45pt;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,255);&quot;&gt;https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/r/&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.45pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;conda config --add channels &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.45pt;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,255);&quot;&gt;https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/msys2/&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.45pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;conda config --add channels &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.45pt;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,255);&quot;&gt;https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud/conda-forge/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="190" width="392.5" x="670" y="230" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--42" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--39" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--41" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--39" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;执行以下命令看是否配置成功：conda config --show&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="120" x="806.25" y="480" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--44" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--41" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--43" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--41" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="下面开始安装RKNN-Toolkit2和更新RKNPU2的连板推理运行库（rknn-toolkit2是基于python实现的模型转换工具，可将其他模型转换成RKNN格式，并提供有限的推理接口；而rknpu2是板端的组件，提供npu驱动，并基于C语言提供模型加载、模型推理等功能。）" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="130" width="163.75" x="784.38" y="600" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--46" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--43" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--45" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--43" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;align=left;" value="&lt;font&gt;打开github网站：&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;https://github.com/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;airockchip/rknn-toolkit2，从Release中选择一个RKNN-TOOLKIT2版本下载下来(比如版本2.3.2)，在ubuntu系统中使用unzip解压。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="66.13" width="270.62" x="730.9399999999999" y="774.37" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--48" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--45" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--47">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--45" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="&lt;b&gt;更新npu连板推理运行库：&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;使用以下两条指令将rknpu2目录下的runtime目录下的librknnrt.so和rknn_server等三个文件(总共4个文件)拷贝到板子上的/usr/lib和/usr/bin下：&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.45pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;adb push runtime/Linux/librknn_api/aarch64/librknnrt.so&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;/usr/lib&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.45pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;adb push runtime/Linux/rknn_server/aarch64/usr/bin/*&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;/usr/bin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90" width="410.62" x="660.9399999999999" y="900" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--50" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--47" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--49" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--47" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="&lt;font&gt;进入板子，给与可执行权限并重启服务：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;chmod +x /usr/bin/rknn_server&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;chmod +x /usr/bin/start_rknn.sh&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;chmod +x /usr/bin/restart_rknn.sh&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;restart_rknn.sh&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90" width="288" x="1242" y="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--52" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--49" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--51" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--49" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=center;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;rounded=0;" value="&lt;b&gt;开始安装&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;rknn-roolkit2&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="67.5" width="166" x="1303" y="211.25" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--54" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--51" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--53" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--51" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;align=left;" value="基于前面我们安装的anaconda，现新建一个conda虚拟python3.11的虚拟环境用于安装rknn-toolkit2，执行以下命令：&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.45pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;conda create --name py3.11-tk2-2.3.2 python=3.11&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90" width="232" x="1270" y="320" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--56" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--53" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--55" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--53" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font&gt;前面我们已经下载了rknn-toolkit2，先进入到：&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;rknn-toolkit2-2.3.2/rknn-toolkit2/packages文件夹，然后在该文件夹下执行以下指令来启动前面创建的conda虚拟python环境：conda activate py3.11-tk2-2.3.2(注意一定要在packages文件夹下启动python环境)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="80" width="277" x="1247.5" y="460" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--58" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--55" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--57" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--55" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font&gt;安装rknn-toolkit2之前要先安装相依赖库，执行以下指令来安装:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;pip install -r x86_64/requirements_cp311-2.3.2.txt -i &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple/ (-i后面是指定pip的下载镜像源为清华源，打开&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;requirements_cp311-2.3.2.txt 可以看到&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;这是瑞芯微推荐的下载源，如果下载失败，可切换其他源尝试)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="110" width="316" x="1228" y="610" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--60" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--57" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--59" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--57" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="依然在packages目录下，conda虚拟python环境下，执行以下命令来安装rknn-toolkit2：&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;pip install x86_64/rknn_toolkit2-2.3.2-cp311-cp311-manylinux_2_17_x86_64.manylinux2014_x86_64.whl&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="85.07" width="301" x="1235.5" y="780" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--59" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font&gt;执行以下指令来安装tensorflow和onnx(安装完才支持转换这两种模型)：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;pip3 install tensorflow==2.14.0 -i &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;pip3 install onnx==1.17.0 -i &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;(一定按照指定版本安装，否则可能会报依赖错误)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="130" width="321" x="1225.5" y="910" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--61" parent="1" style="ellipse;shape=cloud;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;align=left;" value="&lt;font&gt;这里安装完，我测试模型转换的时候，遇到一个报错：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;ModuleNotFoundError: No module named &amp;amp;#39;pkg_resources&amp;amp;#39，这是由于我的&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;setuptools&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;版本过高导致，使用pip将setuptools工具版本降到80.9.0即可&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="160" width="300" x="970" y="1090" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--62" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--61" style="curved=1;endArrow=classic;html=1;rounded=0;exitX=0.933;exitY=0.475;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;exitPerimeter=0;entryX=0.25;entryY=1;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--59" value="">
          <mxGeometry height="50" relative="1" width="50" as="geometry">
            <Array as="points">
              <mxPoint x="1320" y="1150" />
              <mxPoint x="1270" y="1100" />
            </Array>
            <mxPoint x="1270" y="1150" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="1320" y="1100" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--67" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--64" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--66" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--64" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;align=left;" value="&lt;font&gt;(可选安装)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;下面安装rknn-toolkit-lite2， (这是一个板端的运行组件)，它与rknn-toolkit2的区别是：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Color Emoji&amp;quot;; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;RKNN-Toolkit2&lt;/span&gt;：&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Color Emoji&amp;quot;; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;PC 端全功能开发套件&lt;/span&gt;，负责把 PyTorch/ONNX/TensorFlow 等模型 → 转换成 RKNN 格式，并做量化、调试、性能评估。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Color Emoji&amp;quot;; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;RKNN-Toolkit-Lite2&lt;/span&gt;：&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Color Emoji&amp;quot;; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;板端（RK356x/RK3588 等）轻量 Python 推理库&lt;/span&gt;，&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Color Emoji&amp;quot;; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;只做一件事&lt;/span&gt;：加载已转换好的 &lt;code style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; line-height: 24px; display: inline; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;.rknn&lt;/code&gt; 模型，调用 NPU 做推理。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="170" width="316" x="1680" y="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--65" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--59" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;entryX=0;entryY=0.459;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;entryPerimeter=0;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--64">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--69" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--66" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--68" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--66" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="&lt;font&gt;进入之前下载的rknn-toolkit2，进到&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;rknn-toolkit2-2.3.2/rknn_toolkit_lit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;e2/packages文件夹下，执行以下指令通过adb将whl文件传到板子的/userdata文件夹下：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8.05pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;adb push rknn_toolkit_&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.95pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;lite2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8.05pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;-2.3.2-cp311-cp311-manylinux_2_17_aarch64.manylinux2014_aarch64.whl /userdata&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="110" width="277.5" x="1699.25" y="310" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--71" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--68" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--70" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--68" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="传输完成后，打开板子的串口终端，执行以下指令来安装rknn-toolkit-lite2：&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;pip install rknn_toolkit_lite2-2.3.2-cp311-cp311-manylinux_2_17_aarch64.manylinux2014_aarch64.whl&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="80" width="288" x="1694" y="470" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--73" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--70" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--72" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--70" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;至此，rnkk-toolkit2和rknn-toolkit-lite2均已安装完成，下面开始测试rknn-toolkit2&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="182" x="1747" y="600" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--85" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--72" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--84">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--72" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;下面使用modelzoo来测试rknn-toolit&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;modelzoo:&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;是瑞芯微提供的一系列各种模型的模型集合,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;提供了大量模型转换与部署的示例代码，旨在帮助用户快速在搭载瑞&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;芯微芯片的开发板上运行各种模型。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;modelzoo的下载链接：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);&quot;&gt;htt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);&quot;&gt;ps://github.com/airockchip/rknn_model_zoo，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;下载下来后，在ubuntu中使用unzip解压&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="110" width="303.5" x="1686.25" y="720" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--80" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--74" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--79">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--74" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font&gt;然后使用以下指令导出环境变量，使能编译器：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;export GCC_COMPILER=/opt/atk-dlrv1126b-toolchain/bin/aarch64-buildroot-linux-gnu&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="80" width="231" x="1722.5" y="1000" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--82" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--79" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--81" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--79" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" value="下面以yolov5模型为例，来测试模型的转换、加载、运行、推理：" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="70" width="150" x="2190" y="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--88" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--81" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--87" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--81" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;align=left;" value="先保证ubuntu能访问互联网，然后开始下载onnx模型：&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.45pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;cd&amp;nbsp; rknn_model_zoo-2.3.2/examples/yolov5/model&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.45pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.45pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;sh download_model.sh&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="91.25" width="300" x="2115" y="194.38" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--86" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--84" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--74">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--84" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="解压后会生成datasets、examples、doc、build-linux.sh等文件夹，datasets就是测试使用的数据集，example就是示例代码，build-linux.sh就是编译linux系统开发板的脚本。" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="74.93" width="220" x="1728" y="880" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--90" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--87" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--89" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--87" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="使用以下指令进入之前我们创建的conda环境：&lt;div&gt;conda&amp;nbsp; activate&amp;nbsp; py3.11-tk2-2.3.2&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="78.75" width="185" x="2172.5" y="345" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--92" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--89" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--91" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--89" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="进入yolov5的例程目录下：&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.45pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;cd&amp;nbsp; rknn_model_zoo-2.3.2/examples/yolov5/python&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="78.44" width="187.5" x="2171.25" y="471.56" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--94" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--91" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--93" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--91" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font&gt;使用以下命令进行模型转换(以RV1126B板子为例)：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;python3 convert.py ../model/yolov5s_relu.onnx rv1126b&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;转换完成后，在model目录下就会生成yolov5.rknn文件，至此模型文件就转换完成。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="100.78" width="245" x="2142.5" y="600" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--96" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--93" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--95" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--93" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;rounded=0;" value="然后下一步还要编译推理代码：&lt;div&gt;在modelzoo的顶层目录下，执行以下命令编译瑞芯微提供的C++例程(还是以rv1126b为例)：&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.45pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;./build-linux.sh -t rv1126b -a aarch64 -d yolov5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="88.83" width="235" x="2147.5" y="774.37" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--98" edge="1" parent="1" source="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--95" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" target="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--97">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IWO89DZMRxDcJP3v9Gk--95" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="&lt;font&gt;编译完成后，会在modelzoo下面的&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;install/rv1126b_linux_aarch64/rknn_yolov5_demo 目录下&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;生成&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;可执行文件和打包模型等文件。然后执行以下adb命令将模型和可执行文件等都拷贝到开发板的/userdata/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;aidemo目录&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;下：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.45pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;adb push install/rv1126b_linux_aarch64/rknn_yolov5_demo/ /userdata/aidemo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="127.5" width="302.5" x="2113.75" y="922.5" as="geometry" />
